To configure the in-app purchase, you will need to create a product ID in the Apple App Store Connect. The product ID will be used to identify the in-app purchase item.

**Additional Notes:**

* The code assumes that you have a `Purchases` framework available.
* You can customize the coin values and prices as needed.
* You can add additional features, such as a gambling interface, to the app.
* You will need to submit your app to the Apple App Store.

