* The `NewsService` class manages the news articles and fetches them based on the user's location and demographics.
* The `Article` struct defines the structure of each news article.
* The `ContentView` view displays the list of articles.
* The `onAppear()` method of the `ContentView` view calls the `fetchArticles()` method of the `NewsService` when the view appears.
* The articles are tailored to the user's demographics based on their location and other factors.

